::Aerotaur/Pyrotaur::
       Aerotaur sits down facing Pyrotaur.  "So what do you have to tell me?"

       Pyrotaur sits up.  "You are our leader."  He keeps talking, cutting 
off Aerotaur's question.  "You are Aerotaur.  You were damaged b our former 
leader after an accident where we tried to make him more aggressive.  He shot 
you into space.  You crashed here.  We followed you, as did he.  He is 
somewhere in this area."  He points to the Mediterranean on a map.  "We need 
your help so that we can fix him and become a gestalt again."

--part1_c8.1d11870e.29176508_boundary
